---

## Key Insight

A heap maintains order without fully sorting.

For kth largest:

```text
Max Heap:
pop k times

OR

Min Heap of size k:
keep only k largest elements
```

---

## Complexity

### Max Heap

```text
Time: O(n log n)
Space: O(n)
```

### Min Heap (size k)

```text
Time: O(n log k)
Space: O(k)
```

